==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bony
<hw>Bon"y</hw> <pr>(b⟦omac⟧"n⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Consisting of bone, or of bones; full of bones; pertaining to
bones.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having large or prominent bones.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Bony fish</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>the
menhaden.</cd> -- <col><b>Bony pike</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>,
<cd>the gar pike (<gen>Lepidosteus</gen>).</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bonze</ent>⟦br⟧
